Beautiful.

40:56.025 --> 40:57.859
You should play more.

40:57.860 --> 40:59.695
Oh, I never stop playing.

41:02.165 --> 41:05.250
I compose whole sonatas
in my head, brother.

41:05.251 --> 41:06.951
You had a good day
then, my love?

41:06.953 --> 41:09.204
Mmm. Yes.

41:09.205 --> 41:10.921
A beautiful day.

41:17.714 --> 41:21.683
And here's to an even
better tomorrow.

